videos.headline: Hall coughs up the football to Louisiana
videos.description: Iowa State's Breece Hall runs up the middle for 15 yards but fumbles at the 42-yard line.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hall coughs up the football to Louisiana) 2020/9/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hall's 10-yard gain sets up Nwangwu's goal-line TD
videos.description: Breece Hall gets the offense to the 1-yard line and sets up Kene Nwangwu for an Iowa State touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hall's 10-yard gain sets up Nwangwu's goal-line TD) 2020/9/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ragin' Cajuns return kickoff 95 yards to the house
videos.description: Chris Smith finds space and breaks free for a 95-yard kickoff return touchdown for Louisiana.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ragin' Cajuns return kickoff 95 yards to the house) 2020/9/12

videos.headline: Hall bounces outside for an 11-yard TD run
videos.description: Breece Hall runs to the outside and scores an 11-yard touchdown to give Iowa State a 14-7 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hall bounces outside for an 11-yard TD run) 2020/9/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hutchinson hauls in a leaping grab for ISU
videos.description: Xavier Hutchinson comes down with a great catch between three Louisiana defenders.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hutchinson hauls in a leaping grab for ISU) 2020/9/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Washington fights for the Ragin' Cajun interception
videos.description: Asjlin Washington pulls the catch out of Xavier Hutchinson's hands for a Louisiana interception.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Washington fights for the Rajin' Cajun interception) 2020/9/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lewis hits LeBlanc in stride for a 78-yard TD
videos.description: Levi Lewis drops in a 78-yard dime to Peter LeBlanc, giving Louisiana the lead over Iowa State 17-14.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Lewis hits LeBlanc in stride for a 78-yard TD) 2020/9/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ragin' Cajuns score second return TD of the day
videos.description: Eric Garror finds a free lane on the punt return and books it for an 83-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ragin' Cajuns score second return TD of the day) 2020/9/12 ESHEET
